Among the benefits for the residents of the TOR are the income tax of not more than 5 per cent over the first five years and not less than 10 per cent over the next 5 years, social contributions of 7.6 per cent over 10 years, the use of the free customs zone, the concessional access to various infrastructure facilities, and the discount rates on rent.
